Unitron:



Unitron's body, as well as the ground, shook as the fusion blasts erupted all 
around him.  Some dirt hit his legs, but that was it.  He knew he'd need a 
little something stronger than optic blasts to take down Megatron and his 
fusion cannon.

"Hmmm.  Well, all I can say to that is: You missed Galvatron!" Unitron yelled 
with a chuckle, his laser rifle appearing in his hand from subspace and 
pointing at Megatron.  Three bolts shot out at Megatron's abdomen the 
boosters in Unitron's feet propelled him back and into the air slowly, 
gaining momentum quickly, as he fired upon Megatron.
